					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-8759851#post-4072672</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-8759851/scp-4045#post-4072672</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 01 Dec 2018 01:59:29 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Varaxous</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2433554</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Sometimes, truth is stranger than fiction.</p> <p>In all realness, no I don't have this fetish and was not super aware that this was some big thing. The picture in the author post was a picture a friend sent me when I showed them the article.</p> <p>As for the thought process within, I had no influence from the internet. It went like this:</p> <p>1. Get Ihps draft about women being sexually attracted to cars.<br /> 2. Think about it some and where exactly I wanted to take it.<br /> 3. Maybe the women aren't sexually attracted but physically, like a woman/car magnet.<br /> 4. What if it were both?<br /> 5. This come out.</p> <p>And that's all I wrote and such.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
