					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-8759851#post-4071977</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-8759851/scp-4045#post-4071977</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 30 Nov 2018 08:40:53 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>mickeyten</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4444390</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Well, no alterations aside from, well, the anomaly.</p> <p>There is a lot of creative writing on this site that include paraphilic concepts, many of them fantastic pieces (&quot;The Vorehole&quot; comes to mind), and there's no reason to assume that the author was turning &quot;their fetish&quot; into an SCP. It's fine if you don't like it, but downvoting on that presumption is the bad form here.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-8759851#post-4071938</guid>
